Download the Llama2 7B Chat model from Meta so that you have the following files:

llama-2-7b-chat
llama-2-7b-chat/tokenizer_checklist.chk
llama-2-7b-chat/params.json
llama-2-7b-chat/tokenizer.model
llama-2-7b-chat/checklist.chk
llama-2-7b-chat/consolidated.00.pth

Then install the dependencies:

python3 -m venv .env
pip install -r requirements.txt

And activate the environment:

source .env/bin/activate
